The goal was to ensure that all API endpoints function correctly, focusing on the core functionalities and performance to provide a seamless user experience. ### Configuration: - **Collection Creation:** A Postman Collection was created based on the [API documentation](https://market-final-project.binaracademy.org/api-docs/#/). - **API Endpoints Covered:** The collection contains multiple API requests across various functionalities such as authentication, product management, order processing, wishlist management, and notifications. **Auth:** - `POST /auth/register` - `POST /auth/login` - `GET /auth/user` - `PUT /auth/user` - `PUT /auth/change-password` ``` **Seller - Product:** - `POST /seller/product` - `GET /seller/product` - `GET /seller/product/{id}` - `PUT /seller/product/{id}` - `PATCH /seller/product/{id}` - `DELETE /seller/product/{id}` **Seller - Order:** - `GET /seller/order` - `GET /seller/order/{id}` - `PATCH /seller/order/{id}` - `GET /seller/order/product/{product_id}` **Seller - Category:** - `GET /seller/category` - `GET /seller/category/{id}` **Seller - Banner:** - `GET /seller/banner` - `GET /seller/banner/{id}` **Buyer - Product:** - `GET /buyer/product` - `GET /buyer/product/{id}` **Buyer - Order:** - `POST /buyer/order` - `GET /buyer/order` - `GET /buyer/order/{id}` - `PUT /buyer/order/{id}` - `DELETE /buyer/order/{id}` **Buyer - Wishlist:** - `POST /buyer/wishlist` - `GET /buyer/wishlist` - `GET /buyer/wishlist/{id}` - `DELETE /buyer/wishlist/{id}` **History:** - `GET /history` - `GET /history/{id}` **Notification:** - `GET /notification` - `GET /notification/{id}` - `PATCH /notification/{id}` ``` ### Testing and Results: - **Assertion Testing:** A total of **43 test cases** were created, covering both **positive** and **negative** scenarios. The results for all tests were **Pass**, indicating the API is functioning as expected. - **Web Service Testing:** Apart from functional testing, I conducted web service tests focusing on: - **Security:** Ensuring the API is secure and free from vulnerabilities. - **Request/Response Validation:** Verifying that the data formats are correct and consistent with the API documentation. - **Performance Testing:** Evaluating server performance, response times, and stability under different loads. ### Conclusion: All tests have been successfully completed with positive results. The API for the Second Hand mobile app is fully functional, secure, and ready for release. The performance tests also show the server can handle a large number of requests without issues.
